<i>noun</i>: 만병통치약 [만ː병통치약] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>만병통치약 [만ː병통치약]</dt><br>
<dd>1. panacea; cure-all</dd><br>
<dd>모든 병을 다 고치는 약.</dd><br>
<dd>A medicine that cures every disease.</dd><br>
<dd>2. panacea; remedy for all difficulties</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 여러 가지 경우에 두루 효력을 나타내는 어떤 대책.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state in which a single solution works well for many cases.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>